frames.caption: A majestic whale appears to swim through a starry night sky, illuminated by the ethereal glow of the northern lights. The whale's body shimmers with a cosmic blend of colors, as if it is part of the universe itself.
frames.description: The scene depicts a surreal and fantastical setting where a whale is seen in the night sky, surrounded by stars and the aurora borealis. This creates a dreamlike atmosphere, blending elements of nature and the cosmos.

frames.caption: A majestic cosmic whale glides through a starry night sky, its body shimmering with ethereal lights. The aurora borealis dances around it, casting a mystical glow on the scene.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical setting where a whale, illuminated with cosmic colors, swims through the night sky amidst a backdrop of stars and northern lights. This surreal imagery combines elements of nature and space, creating a dreamlike atmosphere.

frames.caption: A majestic, ethereal creature resembling a whale glides gracefully through a starry cosmic backdrop. The creature's body shimmers with hues of blue and green, blending seamlessly with the surrounding auroras and twinkling stars. Its fins and tail appear translucent, adding to its otherworldly presence.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical marine creature swimming through a space-like environment filled with stars and auroras. The setting is surreal, combining elements of the ocean and outer space to create a dreamlike atmosphere.
